  foreach loop
  streams - java8

forloop:
    keyword : for
    components : intializer, condition, incrementer.
for(int i=1; i<4; i++){
 sout("Hi")
}

iteration :1
    i=1, true, print
iteration :2
    i =2, true, print
iteration :3
    i =2, true, print
iteration :4
    i =2, false

    comes out of loop


Write a program:
 it should take a number
 It has to print the number sequence accordingly
