While Loop:
   Keyword : while
   Components : initializer, condition, increment
Usage: If we want to separate initialization, increment part, then we go with while loop.
   initialization
   while(condition){
     statements;
     .
     .
     .
     incrementer;
   }

   int i=10;
   while(i>0){
   sout(i)
    i--;
   }

-----------------------------------------
Do while Loop:
  Keywords: do, while.
  components: initializer, condition, increment
Usage:
   do{
   statements;
   .
   .
   .
   increment;
   }while(condition)